node_2.subject: Isabella Rodriguez
node_2.description: This is Isabella Rodriguez's plan for Monday February 13: wake up and complete the morning routine at 6:00 am, use the furnace to heat up the cafe and prepare for opening at 7:00 am, serve breakfast to customers from 8:00 am to 10:00 am, take a break to rest and plan for the day at 10:00 am, cook a meal for lunch at 12:00 pm, continue working and interacting with customers until 4:00 pm, close the cafe at 5:00 pm, spend time updating inventory and expenses until 6:00 pm.
